---
<section id="process" aria-labelledby="process-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label" data-i18n="process.label">How We Work</div>
    <h2 class="section-title" id="process-heading" data-i18n="process.title">From zero to live — in days, not months.</h2>
    <p class="section-sub" data-i18n="process.sub">A focused four-step process built around speed, quality, and results.</p>

    <div class="process-grid" role="list">
      <div class="process-step reveal" role="listitem">
        <div class="step-num" aria-hidden="true">01</div>
        <h3 class="step-title" data-i18n="process.s1.title">Audit &amp; Strategy</h3>
        <p class="step-desc" data-i18n="process.s1.desc">We assess your brand, market, competitors, and conversion opportunities. Clear direction before a single pixel is designed.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step reveal reveal-delay-1" role="listitem">
        <div class="step-num" aria-hidden="true">02</div>
        <h3 class="step-title" data-i18n="process.s2.title">Brand &amp; UX Direction</h3>
        <p class="step-desc" data-i18n="process.s2.desc">Identity, visual language, and store architecture defined. Every decision is made with conversion logic at its core.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step reveal reveal-delay-2" role="listitem">
        <div class="step-num" aria-hidden="true">03</div>
        <h3 class="step-title" data-i18n="process.s3.title">Build &amp; Integration</h3>
        <p class="step-desc" data-i18n="process.s3.desc">Store built, pixels fired, flows configured, SEO foundation laid. Everything tested before it touches a customer.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step reveal reveal-delay-3" role="listitem">
        <div class="step-num" aria-hidden="true">04</div>
        <h3 class="step-title" data-i18n="process.s4.title">Launch &amp; Optimize</h3>
        <p class="step-desc" data-i18n="process.s4.desc">Go live with confidence. We monitor, iterate, and optimize based on real data — not assumptions.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
